---
import Layout from '../layouts/main.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Privacy Policy - Public Code US"
	description="Our privacy policy explaining how we protect your data when you sign the petition."
	currentPage="/privacy"
>
	<section class="bg-am-light border-b-4 border-am-dark py-20">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
			<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>

			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">Introduction</h2>
					<p class="font-bold text-am-dark leading-relaxed">
						Public Code US ("we," "us," "our," or "Company") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and sign our petition.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="border-4 border-am-dark bg-am-blue p-6">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">What Information We Collect</h2>
					<p class="font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">When you sign the petition, we collect:</p>
					<ul class="font-bold text-am-dark space-y-2">
						<li>• Full name</li>
						<li>• Email address</li>
						<li>• State of residence</li>
						<li>• ZIP code (optional)</li>
						<li>• Personal message (optional)</li>
						<li>• Your preference for campaign updates</li>
						<li>• Your IP address and user agent (automatically)</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
					<p class="font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">We use the information you provide to:</p>
					<ul class="font-bold text-am-dark space-y-2">
						<li>✓ Verify your signature for ballot initiatives</li>
						<li>✓ Send campaign updates (if you opted in)</li>
						<li>✓ Understand our supporter demographics</li>
						<li>✓ Comply with state ballot measure requirements</li>
						<li>✓ Prevent fraud and duplicate signatures</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="border-4 border-am-dark bg-am-white p-6">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">We Will NOT</h2>
					<ul class="font-bold text-am-dark space-y-2">
						<li>✗ Sell your data to third parties</li>
						<li>✗ Share your email with political candidates</li>
						<li>✗ Share your signature with vendors or advertisers</li>
						<li>✗ Use your information for purposes other than stated above</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">Data Security</h2>
					<p class="font-bold text-am-dark leading-relaxed">
						We implement industry-standard security measures including HTTPS encryption, secure storage, and limited access to your information. However, no system is 100% secure. We recommend using a strong password and updating it regularly.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="border-4 border-am-dark bg-am-red text-am-light p-6">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
					<p class="font-bold mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
					<ul class="font-bold space-y-2">
						<li>• Access your data at any time</li>
						<li>• Remove your signature from the petition</li>
						<li>• Opt out of campaign updates</li>
						<li>• Request deletion of your data</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="font-bold mt-4">Contact us at hello@publiccode.us to exercise these rights.</p>
				</div>

				<div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">Compliance</h2>
					<p class="font-bold text-am-dark leading-relaxed">
						We comply with applicable state and federal privacy laws including GDPR (for European visitors), CCPA (California), and state ballot initiative laws. We may be required to share signature information with state election authorities for ballot qualification purposes.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="border-4 border-am-dark bg-am-light p-6">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-am-dark mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
					<p class="font-bold text-am-dark">
						For privacy concerns or to exercise your rights:<br />
						<strong>Email:</strong> hello@publiccode.us
					</p>
				</div>

				<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-600">
					Last updated: March 2026
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
